---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use" description="Terms of Use for Are You a Heretic?.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-charcoal/70">Last updated: 2026-03-30</p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Educational content only</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Are You a Heretic? provides educational and informational content. It is not legal, theological, pastoral, or professional advice.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">No guarantees</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Content is provided "as is" without warranties of completeness, accuracy, or fitness for a particular purpose.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Acceptable use</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      You agree not to abuse the site, interfere with operation, attempt unauthorized access, or use the site for unlawful activity.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Newsletter and contact forms</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      If you submit forms, you confirm that the information is yours to provide and accurate. Newsletter signup subscribes you to the Probably Theology newsletter, and you can unsubscribe any time.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Intellectual property</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Site content, branding, and original materials are owned by Probably Theology unless otherwise attributed. Do not reproduce or redistribute substantial content without permission.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">External links</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Links to third-party services are provided for convenience. We are not responsible for third-party content, policies, or availability.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal mt-8 mb-3">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-charcoal/80">
      Questions about these terms: <a class="text-crimson underline" href="mailto:openscriptureapp@gmail.com">openscriptureapp@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
